title: Rip Off Comix # 1-31 (Rip Off Press)
description:
Underground comic book that reached a rather empressive volumu of 31 issues
Published by Rip Off Press 1977-1991

Rip Off Comix featured Freak Brothers,the Pinhead and similar mainstays, but included a lot of imported material and a few articles of cultural spotlight

Maybe they got a little inspired by what Raw tried to do?

Contributors included:
Gilbert Shelton, Bill Griffith, Jack Jackson, Dan O'Neill, Krystine Kryttre, Richard Sala, Mario Hernandez, Julie Doucet, Michael T. Gilbert, Alan Moore, Eddie Campbell, Savage Pencil, Dori Seda, Spain Rodriquez, Justin Green, J.R. Williams, Carol Lay, Larry Welz, Frank Stack, Mary Fleener, Dennis Worden, Guy Colwell, Trina Robbins, Hunt Emerson and more
